folder: City Island Avenue & Marine Street, Bronx, NY
original_title: Bronx: City Island Avenue - Marine Street
text:
(1)
88 City Island Avenue (City Island); at the S.E. corner of Marine Street, showing the Upper Bronx Community Center. The City Island branch office of the Western Union Telegraph Company is also located here.
Summer, 1923

P. L. Sperr

(2)
The same, at a later date. The Marine Restaurant occupies the house.

July 6, 1936

P. L. Sperr
